{"type": "article", "id": 44967, "title": "时尚杂志《Nylon》停刊，以及，纽约时装周上 Desigual 的走秀很有趣 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-09-08T03:27:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7048, "name": "纽约时装周"}, {"id": 21934, "name": "Nylon"}, {"id": 34833, "name": "Desigual"}, {"id": 10763, "name": "CLOT"}, {"id": 686, "name": "adidas"}, {"id": 43899, "name": "胶带"}, {"id": 37120, "name": "Acne Studio"}, {"id": 43900, "name": "Interparfums"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170908100410cHdgZvlFrEou903V.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-japan-economy-gdp/japans-second-quarter-economic-growth-revised-down-from-stellar-first-reading-idUSKCN1BI373\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>香水制造商 Interparfums 上半年净利润大涨 68%</strong></a> | 受 Jimmy Choo、Coach 等新款香水的业绩拉动，法国香水制造商 Interpardums 上半年销售额同比上涨 29% 至 2.09 亿欧元，净利润则增长了 68%，至 2170 万欧元。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/media/nylon-to-shutter-print-edition-10974257/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>美国时尚杂志《Nylon》纸质版停刊</strong></a> | 《Nylon》宣布纸质版停刊，10 月刊将是最后一期 。同时，《Nylon》将开除印刷厂员工，未来将完全向数字化转型，通过视频、社交媒体和创意吸引更多的年轻读者。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>庆祝 2017 德国啤酒节，<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/technology/adidas-beer-proof-sneakers-oktoberfest-09-07-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">adidas 推出了全新的 pröst 运动鞋</a>。这双鞋以经典的 münchen 为原型，鞋身采用了高质量的牛皮制作。最特别的一点是，它的鞋面可以防止被啤酒和呕吐物弄脏。adidas 说，现在你们可以尽情享受啤酒节了。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908105730RJ50LjpoDuzSYKth.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908105732zU5vEb1RxlOjH8Vs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908105731OZEgcr397NueD82f.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908105731gF4H8MCl5ozZeyaj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600244\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908105731WqwBV5KRSE1NdLgD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600300\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709081057353VZAN8BqmYgvlrsO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.600244\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>时尚界最近刮起了胶带潮流，比如上个月我们刚刚写过的 Raf Simons 的天价胶带。 </p><p>如果你是个漫画迷的话，曾获得 2016 年国誉设计大奖的 Manga Tape 或许你会喜欢。这款胶带设计成了分格漫画的形式，你可以随意画上一个小场景，做成包装的一部分也很讨人喜欢。Manga Tape 将于 9 月 13 日正式登陆<a href=\"http://www.kokuyo-shop.jp/shop/category_list.aspx?CD=F2000073&amp;View=lnkbImageList&amp;Sort=default&amp;Init=true\" rel=\"nofollow\">国誉网店</a>，售价 900 日元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908105757Z25WaKqzUVyB1cHb.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908105822sMa19kc3wKtCIr2D.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908105825l3ufBWFbcIhVr5QC.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908105821zFn5PdcBZtJaXYm2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.965625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/9/acne-studios-showpiece-collection-2017\" rel=\"nofollow\">Acne Studio 推出了全球限量 100 件的收藏级 Showpiece Prototype 系列</a>，该系列所有单品都来自 2017 秋冬系列秀场上的手制成衣。现已登陆纽约 Madison Ave 旗舰店，随后将登陆伦敦 Dover Street 旗舰店、20 日于米兰 Piazza del Carmine 旗舰店以及 26 日于巴黎 Rue Froissart 旗舰店。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908105847WD4RZJQhNSIl3jVH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908105847Efu21F3yAaIjGk0U.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908105848F1B3Qcg7dGebryhi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908105851ak9Sb7yz3u2pJWxm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908105857EzlRf3Pgeo8qiwjG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908105857k5jDntBSTJLRWiAN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>CLOT 联手 Converse，推出了特别联名款 ONE STAR。这双鞋由陈冠希和 Kevin Poon 操刀，以“阴阳”为灵感，采用了起绒反毛皮鞋面，鞋侧部位还有三个代表能量的阴阳符号。 </p><p>这双联名款 ONE STAR 将于 9 月 13 日登陆 JUICE 上海店。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908105910RTAdmawcGtYxWspK.png\" data-ratio=\"0.560582\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908110227ehTmkH9JlzVSwibK.png\" data-ratio=\"0.662226\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908110227cHeGiDj5FvCnEwQB.png\" data-ratio=\"0.651965\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908110228UjVA5wvmdrfgKpFG.png\" data-ratio=\"0.665076\" data-format=\"png\"> </figure></div><p>纽约时装周上，Jean-Paul Goude 任创意总监的<a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/news/2017-09-08/desigual-ny/gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Desigual 发布了全新系列</a>。有意思的是，模特并没有走秀，而是在 T 台上跳起了舞，台风很活泼。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908110008GNxeqdOT4MumC85J.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709081100110AnJaluLCpD1zRvN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908110012Yc3ZxTXzH26MBv91.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908110012yY1GrKQP4vSW5THl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908110013KTZVaNbBnIYDjdFq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908110012eCE8vkFVUojhJb5L.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908110013xvLjEmgeyFHlQ4aK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908110013chRVKreEXqnLjTsg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2017090811001438dY4BNciS9jxkPf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709081100144IRl6zx0jpdJsikf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201709081100144gPJDClOYhiHxwkM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170908110015OYr4oyB80S2WH5f7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：<a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/news/2017-09-08/desigual-ny/gallery/\" rel=\"nofollow\">fashionsnap</a></p>"}